@startuml event-driven-signal-flow-local
!theme plain
!include ../shared/theme.puml
!include ../shared/sequence-theme.puml
title Event-Driven Signal Flow: Local Path

actor User
participant "Card\n(UI Node)" as Card
participant "CardBuffer /\nScrollContainer" as Buffer
participant "CardManager\n(local rules)" as CM

User -> Card : drag/drop interaction
Card -> Card : _get_drag_data()\nemit card_grabbed(card)
User -> Buffer : drop card on target
Buffer -> CM : emit card_placed_in_slot(card, slot)\nor card_dropped_card_container
CM -> CM : _on_card_placed_in_container() /\n_on_card_placed_in_slot():\nincrement move_count, start timer,\nvalidate sorting order

note right of CM
Local in-process signals keep
UI interaction and rule validation
responsive without network coupling.
end note

@enduml

